      <title>随着经济从石油转向多元化，海湾地区 IPO 需求飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/gulf-ipos-see-soaring-demand-as-economies-diversify-from-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东地区经济摆脱对石油的依赖，实现多元化，投资者纷纷涌向中东地区的首次公开募股 (IPO)，零售、美容、医疗保健等各类企业都在准备上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/gulf-ipos-see-soaring-demand-as-economies-diversify-from-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 13:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
